{"type": "article", "id": 20499, "title": "像帽子一样的动物小窝", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-11T07:24:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607133800Al0wxHTt6jWcR2Uy.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\thowlpot 是韩国一家专为小动物做设计的品牌，包块床、皮带、颈圈等物件。HOWLY 像是将布面口袋放在了地上，一侧是封口的，另一侧有一个圆形的开口，里面放有软垫。它可以是小动物的床，也可以是玩乐的物品，因为没有使用金属结构却能保持一个特别的造型，有些像一顶帽子，是类似洞穴的居住环境，显得格外居家。这里是<a href=\"http://howlpot.com/\" target=\"_blank\">工作室主页</a>和<a href=\"http://howlpot.com/product/shopping.html\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133758Nh6MZe7nOqKUVDwi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67237164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133759qk247RtohZNMmuBE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67237164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133759N4vCafPxdkRgqjtw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67237164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133759uvAqa3pZXxsnr1lo.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67237164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}